</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In the dumb theater of Elon Musk=E2=80=
=99s deal to buy Twitter Inc., this week Musk is <a href=3D"https://link.ma=
il.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28001654.264606/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJn=
